msg: Revert the part of r1389031 that made one of the 'svn mergeinfo' tests start
testing the new graphical summary output.  Rationale: that test should keep
doing what it was doing before, which is most directly achieved by adding
the '--show-revs=merged' option; and the graphical summary is in early
development and subject to change considerably so it is not yet useful to
test that it remains the same.
(no_mergeinfo): Remove the graph-shaped expected output and restore the
original blank expectation; add the '--show-revs=merged' option.
